      "lang": "pt",
      "source": "wikidata"
    },
    {
      "text": "Spyro 2: Season of Flame is a 2002 platform game developed by Digital Eclipse and published by Universal Interactive for the Game Boy Advance. It is the fifth installment in the Spyro video game series and a sequel to Spyro: Season of Ice. The game's story centers on the abduction of the Dragon Realm's fireflies at the hands of the Rhynocs, causing the dragons to lose their ability to breathe fire. The protagonist of the story, Spyro the Dragon, must recover the fireflies and uncover the culprit behind the firefly theft.\nThe game received generally favorable reviews from critics, many of whom considered the game to be superior to Spyro: Season of Ice, though the game was criticized for its \"tricky\" controls.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Spyro 2: Season of Flame est un jeu vidéo de plates-formes sorti le 18 octobre 2002 exclusivement sur Game Boy Advance. Il fait partie de la série Spyro the Dragon.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    },
    {
      "text": "Spyro 2: Season of Flame (o più semplicemente Spyro: Season of Flame) è un videogioco a piattaforme per Game Boy Advance della serie Spyro the Dragon, sviluppato da Digital Eclipse e pubblicato da Universal Interactive Studios. È stato pubblicato in Nord America il 25 settembre e in Europa il 3 ottobre 2002. A differenza dell'originale, non è stato commercializzato in Giappone.",
      "lang": "it",
      "source": "wikipedia_it"
    },
    {
      "text": "Spyro 2: Season of Flame — видеоигра в жанре платформер, разработанная Digital Eclipse и изданная Universal Interactive Studios эксклюзивно для Game Boy Advance. Она была выпущена в 2002 году в США и Европе.\nSpyro 2: Season of Flame уже пятая игра в серии Spyro и является прямым продолжением Spyro: Season of Ice. В игре Спайро необходимо освободить всех светлячков и найти того, кто украл их.",
      "lang": "ru",
      "source": "wikipedia_ru"
    },
    {
      "text": "『Spyro 2: Season of Flame』は、2002年にデジタル・エクリプスが開発し、ユニバーサル・インタラクティブからゲームボーイアドバンス向けに発売されたプラットフォームゲームである。本作は『Spyro』ビデオゲームシリーズの5作目であり、『Spyro: Season of Ice』の続編にあたる。物語は、ライノックたちによってドラゴンレルムの蛍が誘拐され、それによってドラゴンたちが炎を吐く能力を失ってしまうという出来事を中心に展開する。主人公のドラゴン、スパイロは、失われた蛍を取り戻し、蛍を盗んだ犯人を突き止めることを目指す。\n本作は批評家から概ね好意的な評価を受け、多くの批評家が『Spyro: Season of Ice』よりも優れていると評したが、「操作が難しい」という点で批判されることもあった。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "ai_local_gemma4",
      "base_lang": "en"
    }
  ]
